50|$|The London Regional Transport (<b>Penalty</b> <b>Fares)</b> Act 1992 and the Greater London Authority Act 1999 allows Transport for London {{to charge}} <b>penalty</b> <b>fares</b> under similar but not {{identical}} rules {{to those on}} National Rail services.|$|R
